						               													<description>Roll and write that tries to diver a dungeon crawler solo game experience that fits in the back of a business card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player tries to defeat a monster, fighting or running away each turn. But, as he fails the attack or decides to run, the stress increases since there are limited options to do this. Decisions can be hard, although the game is very simple. Push your luck mechanisms and dice rolling provide uncertainty and deliver simple and meaningful choices.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a free-to-play roll-and-write game. Print the file or draw the squares and play it immediately. The author developed this idea during a conference when waiting to deliver his communication. Because he had no card to give when he attended Essen Spiel 2022 as Press. An Adventure on the Card is an example of how analogue games can be applied to anything and anywhere.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
